author: @ca_xq4
text:
To LE SSERAFIM,

From the heart of Riyadh, we’re sending you a message full of love, longing, and admiration. You’re not just a music group — you’re an inspiration. Your voices, your energy, and your presence bring light into our lives, even from miles away.

Riyadh misses you, and your fans here dream of the day you step on stage in our city. We want to sing with you, cheer for you, and share a moment that will live in our hearts forever.

We truly believe you can feel the love we hold for you… but if you come here, you'll see it with your own eyes.

Please make Riyadh a stop in your journey — let’s create unforgettable memories together.
We’re waiting for you, with open hearts and open arms.

With all our love,
Your fans in Riyadh
